('37885','13534','5','Exceptional superlative luxury villa in exclusive location in Santa Ponsa '),
('37886','13535','5','This extravagant villa, which is one of the most exclusive real estate properties in the Mediterranean, is situated in a quiet top location, just a few minutes drive away from the prestigious marina of Port Adriano. Five beautiful golf courses are in direct proximity. From every room you will enjoy spectacular and unobstructed South-West sea views. The plot and the terraces of the villa are not visible from the outside. The large terraces are directly accessible from every room. \r\nThis magnificent property has a living space of approximately 1000m ² and wide and open living and dining room, a modern and exclusive spherical kitchen, five large bedrooms, each with Jacuzzi and shower as well as dressing room and two further large, representative rooms. Furthermore, there is a cloak room, a panic room, a guest toilet, extra dressing room and several storage rooms and a cellar. \r\nAn apartment with separate entrance, modern kitchen, living room, bedroom and bath can be used for guests or staff. If necessary, the property offers up to eight bedrooms. \r\nAnother highlight of this extraordinary residence are two large exclusive superimposed swimming pools, the outside-Jacuzzi as well as the panoramic lift. The villa offers a spacious two-car garage and parking space for another five cars. \r\nThe villa is very solidly built, using the most precious and finest materials. Over 70m² 24-carat gold was used in the swimming pools and on the house itself. Everything, from the gold fixtures and crystal chandeliers to the modern and extravagant kitchen was all installed by specialists. The most modern technology and safety equipment meet even the highest expectations, while still being easy to operate. Marble, gold plating and murals round off this luxury villa.If you would like to have more information about the property, please send us an email with your postal address and a landline number and we will contact you directly.'),
